    type: "Combat",
    approach: "Power",
    skill: "Hand-to-Hand",
    flavor: "A weapon is only as secure as the grip behind it. Sometimes it is simply a matter of hitting hard enough that holding on becomes impossible, and even the most disciplined fighter loses their hold.",
