  "Sniper's Advantage": {
    rank: 3,
    type: "Combat",
    approach: "Fortune",
    skill: "Firearms",
    flavor: "At extreme ranges, a bullet strikes home long before the initial gunshot can be heard. Skilled snipers can take advantage of this fact to take their target unaware.",
    description: """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>Once per scene as an Attack and Movement action using a weapon with an ideal range of 5 or greater, you may make a <strong>Firearms (Fortune)</strong> check targeting one character at range 6 or greater. The TN of this check is equal to your target's vigilance.</p>
