    """
  },
  "ICE Breaker": {
    rank: 2,
    type: "Electronic Warfare",
    approach: "Power",
    skill: "Computers",
    flavor: "Network security programs are built to be resilient, redundant, and relentless. A purpose-built kill program is built to be faster. The contest between intrusion countermeasures and the tools designed to shatter them is an arms race with no finish line, and today's unbreakable defense is tomorrow's solved problem.",
    description: """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As an Attack action, make a <strong>Computers [Power] check</strong> at the network's TN.</p>
      <h3>Effects:</h3>
      <p>On success, deal damage equal to your EW Rating plus your Power plus bonus successes to a sentry on your current node. This damage ignores the first 2 points of the sentry's Integrity for the purpose of determining whether it is fragged.</p>
