  "Murderous Intent": {
    rank: 2,
    type: "Combat",
    approach: "Power",
    skill: null,
    flavor: "Combat is, in the most pure essence, the act of killing before being killed. A fighter who embraces that fact, who does not flinch at the thought of taking a life, can tap into a well of primal ferocity that makes them a terrifying opponent.",
    description: """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As an attack and Movement action using a readied weapon, you may make a <strong> TN 4 Combat (Power)</strong> check using the appropriate skill for that weapon.</p>
