    description: """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As an Attack and Movement action using one readied weapon without the Cumbersome quality, you may make a <strong>TN 3 (Power)</strong> check using the appropriate Combat skill for your weapon, targeting one character at range 0–1.</p>
